node.text:
Kjerringøy is a half hour drive north of Bodø, sheltered from the ocean by a garland of small islands, rocks and skerries 🗺 Travel tip: the cycle-route between Bodø and Kjerringøy is rated as Norway's third finest cycleroute.
Photos by @janfinstad
